  {
    "hotel_id": "446522",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/hotelette-seoul-station/hotel/seoul-kr.html",
    "name": "Hotelette Seoul station",
    "detail": "Hotelette was a great place to stay for me, and overall I was very happy I stayed here. I was coming back through Seoul on my way home and wanted a cheap, clean, and convenient place to stay for a day and a night before I went back to the airport. Hotelette is run by a very friendly and helpful woman who keeps the place very clean. Yes the rooms are small (just like a lot of hotels in Korea, Japan, etc.), a/c worked great, wifi was strong, bed was comfortable, and the bathroom was very clean. Room had a little flat screen TV, and a little tower of shelves to put your stuff on. Being right next to Seoul Station makes it an extremely convenient place to stay. If you are arriving from the subway system, just take exit 10 and at the top of the stairs look right. If you are coming from the Airport Train you will need to go all the way up to the 2nd floor of Seoul Station(where all the shops, cafes, and ticket booths are), walk through the area to exit 2, go down the two escalators into the subway area, and then take exit 10. It's actually very easy, and even easier when you are going to the airport as the entrance to the all stop airport train is right by exit 10. ",
